Lesson 4 - Terrain\
\
Right now our scene has a sky but nothing else. Unity has support for terrains, so let's add one.\
\
Create a terrain from either the GameObject menu [A] or the hierarchy view's create menu [B]. Note that these menus are the same, except the former allows you to also create empty game objects, which are useful for organizing our scene.\
\
