Note that trees do not appear in the hierarchy view as children of the terrain game object. Unity has special handling for terrains and trees (and bushes and grass) to achieve acceptable performance.\
\
Unity also has a Tree Creator which you can use to create your own trees. Also there are trees and other terrain decorations available in the asset store.\
